dct_title_s: Wisconsin Wetland Inventory Milwaukee County, Wisconsin 2005
dct_description_sm: The polygon and point data layers both represent wetlands for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2005. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, MilwaukeeCounty_Wetlands_2005.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources in 2007.
